{"tid":837211,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【有片】網傳中山巴士女乘客遭男子猥褻　大哭求助卻無人理會　","createTime":"2018-09-26T08:04:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-26T08:58:08.000Z","uid":176442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b797f2abde3d0b719950d26f1916f7bd46f51ede","tid":837211,"uid":176442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T08:04:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%A4%A7%E5%9C%8B%E5%B0%8F%E4%BA%8B/239921/%E6%9C%89%E7%89%87-%E7%B6%B2%E5%82%B3%E4%B8%AD%E5%B1%B1%E5%B7%B4%E5%A3%AB%E5%A5%B3%E4%B9%98%E5%AE%A2%E9%81%AD%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E7%8C%A5%E8%A4%BB-%E5%A4%A7%E5%93%AD%E6%B1%82%E5%8A%A9%E5%8D%BB%E7%84%A1%E4%BA%BA%E7%90%86%E6%9C%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25B0%258F%25E4%25BA%258B%2F239921%2F%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%2589%2587-%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E5%2582%25B3%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25B1%25B1%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E4%25B9%2598%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E9%2581%25AD%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25AD%2590%25E7%258C%25A5%25E8%25A4%25BB-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%2593%25AD%25E6%25B1%2582%25E5%258A%25A9%25E5%258D%25BB%25E7%2584%25A1%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%2590%2586%25E6%259C%2583&d=vqf9ZX9Fm6encRDPqvqyrMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=89eeae40\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%A4%A7%E5%9C%8B%E5%B0%8F%E4%BA%8B/239921/%E6%9C%89%E7%89%87-%E7%B6%B2%E5%82%B3%E4%B8%AD%E5%B1%B1%E5%B7%B4%E5%A3%AB%E5%A5%B3%E4%B9%98%E5%AE%A2%E9%81%AD%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E7%8C%A5%E8%A4%BB-%E5%A4%A7%E5%93%AD%E6%B1%82%E5%8A%A9%E5%8D%BB%E7%84%A1%E4%BA%BA%E7%90%86%E6%9C%83</a><br />\n<br />\n昨天日（25日）晚，網傳廣東中山市一架巴士上發生猥褻女性事件。從網傳影片可見，一名女子由巴士後座沖向後車門試圖逃離，卻遭一男子強行抱回後座。期間女子大聲哭叫，但周圍乘客與司機始終未有勸阻。據發布影片的網友稱，影片轉自微信群，自己並不是目擊者。平安中山官方微博今日表示，對於網傳女子於巴士上遭遇猥褻事件，當地警方已經介入調查。<br />\n<br />\n隨著影片被大量轉發，不少網民都對影片中被猥褻女子的安危感到擔憂，亦有不少網民認為周邊乘客冷血無情。<br />\n<br />\n網民熱議：<br />\n<br />\n「我打開視頻後。內心一緊。那個哭聲 我現在也忘不掉。」<br />\n<br />\n「最讓人絕望的是路人的漠視以待。」<br />\n<br />\n「這女孩子穿的也很樸素了吧，也沒有晚上出門吧，也沒有上私家車吧，然而怎麼樣呢？」<br />\n<br />\n「這一車的人都是瞎子嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n「再也沒臉說印度了，因為這輛公車上的中國人不配。」<br />\n<br />\n「現在的社會，世態炎涼啊。」"},{"pid":"a2f7968ab992563575a21ec7b976bddc47e103d5","tid":837211,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T08:07:52.000Z","msg":"中國人就是個支那劣種"},{"pid":"63480546e294bbd123295b1b4c620c9313cf496f","tid":837211,"uid":166785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T08:09:25.000Z","msg":"都說天足同支那一撚樣"},{"pid":"1899a9711ebeeab69b55a7faa24137df82d1a581","tid":837211,"uid":144378,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T08:10:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"27f96e3a1afaea041d53a4b5a571460166a38a34","tid":837211,"uid":76314,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T08:40:40.000Z","msg":"睇個款，應該姦埋都無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"169e29c0b7d16f94b90378e6cc72148590b8c219","tid":837211,"uid":120935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T08:43:47.000Z","msg":"沒事沒事 別看"},{"pid":"3a8c578b7f5849cad15b3f644df330935c2ee0d7","tid":837211,"uid":9965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T08:43:47.000Z","msg":"聽講大陸只要唔係強姦就無事，最多坐十幾日<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ac77de2350bd0a22151de320ce43561bf01d43c","tid":837211,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T08:45:31.000Z","msg":"符合"},{"pid":"992f7bf0b0b4fb239d133018c4f3c0c036ae2ecc","tid":837211,"uid":60668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T08:58:08.000Z","msg":"中山大笨象"}]}